Class ViaRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • rules.ViaRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ObjectInfoPanel.Printable, java.io.Serializable

    public class ViaRule
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, ObjectInfoPanel.Printable
    Contains an array of vias used for routing. Vias at the beginning of the array are preferred to later vias.
